      "content": "it's just... it's not just sadness. it's like the color has been completely drained out of everything. i look at my food, my bed, my work, and it all just feels so pointless. like i'm just a ghost walking through a life i don't even want anymore. i'm just so tired of fighting to feel okay when there's nothing left to feel for.",
